{"type": "article", "id": 25498, "title": "3D 打印剃须刀", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-15T07:10:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702120452P7GysR92hTc8wjgV.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是通过 3D 打印完成的剃须刀，它并不能转动头部，需要通过手动来调整角度。钛金属的材质和简洁的外形让它拥有一份硬朗的气息，没有塑料之类的配件，更加坚固耐用。设计者是来自荷兰的团队 RZR 和设计师 Patrick Schuur，他们希望做成可持续使用的剃须刀。产品目前在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/992104484/rzr-shaving-combining-both-beauty-and-comfort?ref=nav_search\">这里是众筹链接</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120450zF1UVx5aACiThomJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.48899756\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120450hVlPFQmBugfsRWN4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48899756\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120451OvXFLdMls93b70cI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48899756\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120451jmAVxMFcO7fso8Nk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48899756\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}